Reports
..................................................................

All > Reports > View/Run 
All > Reports > Getting Started 
Column Context Menu -> generate Reports

...................................................................

Report Types:
    25 standard types + 3

Modifying existing report is beneficial

....................................................................

Report visibility:
    My reports , Group , Global , All 

....................................................................

Report Designer:
    Easily create report
    Sections:
        Data -> Data Source
        Type -> Report Type (28 types)
        Configure -> Group data, run calculations 
        Style -> Adjust looks 
    System tables are restricted from reporting

.....................................................................

Report Actions and Options:
    Info , sharing menu , Delete report , Save report , Run report 
    update, Insert, insert and stay, Save as report source 

......................................................................

Report Distribution:
    Sharing -> Publish 
    copy report link 
    open url 

Sharing menu:
    Share 
    Schedule 
    add to dashboard 
    Export to PDF 
    Publish 

.......................................................................

Add to dashboard:
    All > reports > View/Run 
    Sharing -> Add to dashboard -> add 

