.............................................................................

Creating Notifications:
    When to send:
        Record inserted or updated 
        Event is fired 
        Triggered 
        Script

    Who will recieve
    What will it contain 

.............................................................................

Email Layouts and Templates:
    Create Email Layout : All > system Policy > Email > Layouts
    Apply Layout to Email Template: All > System Notification > Email > Templates 
    Apply Template to Notification: All > System Notification > Email > Notifications 


Email Layout -> HTML Content [sys_email_layout]

